'''Bestrum algae''' was an [[Water/Legends|aquatic]] [[Species/Legends|species]] of [[Algae/Legends|algae]] native to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Baralou]]. It was harvested with sealed [[aquapod]]s and processed into [[Foodstuff/Legends|food]]. One of the harvesting plants on the planet, [[Aqualis Base]], was actually a front for the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]], which was supplied with many foodstuffs made from the algae.

